ActBoards of Trade Act
SubjectChambre de commerce au Coeur de la Montérégie - Quebec ** Change of Boundaries **
PrecisOrder approving the application by the CHAMBRE DE COMMERCE AU COEUR DE LA MONTÉRÉGIE, in Quebec, to CHANGE THE BOUNDARIES of its district from the Marieville, Sainte-Angèle-de-Monnoir, Rougemont and St-Césaire to Marieville, Rougemont, Saint-Césaire, Sainte-Angèle-de-Monnoir, Saint-Paul d'Abbotsford and Ange-Gardien.
